data.eml:eml: A new intertidal octopus species, Octopus incella (Cephalopoda: Octopodidae), from Okinawa, southern Japan

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Kaneko, Natsumi, Kubodera, Tsunemi (2007): A new intertidal octopus species, Octopus incella (Cephalopoda: Octopodidae), from Okinawa, southern Japan. Zootaxa 1140: 39-49, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.175107
